{"tid":2462184,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【當年今日】天水圍新市鎮開幕","createTime":"2021-03-26T00:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T03:35:23.000Z","uid":10540,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"784889fc66b22e2aacea1b018d8dca6ebec12d1a","tid":2462184,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:21:45.000Z","msg":"1993年3月26日，港英政府為新界西北的天水圍新市鎮舉行開幕儀式，同時進行輕鐵通車典禮。開幕儀式在剛落成的天水圍公園舉行，由時任港督彭定康連同一眾高官共同參與。當港督到訪天耀邨時，一批居民反對在新市鎮內設置殯儀館，而港督繼續與市民握手回應。<br />\n（政府新聞處圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcEvsenjRVo5T1N8YWecy1Emhd48ApbwhDmcdsrUT1fT7?filename=wmmUAH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmmUAH8.jpg&h=6ecd8eb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVqN8cGzJigHJ4rSp47g6MtMjndxMBsqPgLM5J4Kghyq7?filename=XDwxnob.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDwxnob.jpg&h=f6d19cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcKEbjNHoPt8qrxdQstsBXSXbV28A5brLyWNUhxtaLfur?filename=uETWO3r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuETWO3r.jpg&h=6350d44b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbuCyFQfvAG3LQwSKoR7dc7nHFJ6XXWmpPrzXBsLdjuJD?filename=L0Bxnof.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0Bxnof.jpg&h=fb427678&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"514990815c9f1096197df448ee2a6e16e9c21a39","tid":2462184,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:24:07.000Z","msg":"差唔多三十年<br />\n<br />\n肥彭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051fdecb6b15d63b5a70b5c84996d074dcd20acf","tid":2462184,"uid":2247,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:24:46.000Z","msg":"第3 張相入面市民既笑容自97 淪陷後冇再出現過"},{"pid":"7d134fb66559f2b9e1d2fd16f7b4f7b4ad7446f4","tid":2462184,"uid":99962,"like":8,"dislike":0,"